, the quadrate distal antennal segments would suggest that the specimen might be 
<specimenCount id="9D4BFD0FFFB5FFB5FAD31778C204496F" box="[1366,1387,1060,1083]" pageId="55" pageNumber="56" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
